(Lesson Vocabulary) Tj
T*
(- Novel: The main topic being studied, understood here as novel study develops) Tj
T*
(understanding of plot, character, setting, and theme in long prose texts.) Tj
T*
(- Core Focus: The main idea the learner must understand in this lesson: story) Tj
T*
(development and critical interpretation.) Tj
T*
(- Application: The point where the explanation is used in practice, such as tracking how) Tj
T*
(a character changes across chapters.) Tj
T*
(- Common Error: A repeated learner difficulty in this topic, for example telling the) Tj
T*
(story without analyzing its meaning.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
